tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE customer_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    rating INT,
    comment TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE customer_feedback (
    feedback_id SERIAL,
    customer_id INT,
    rating INT,
    comment VARCHAR(255),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE feedback_analysis (
  analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  rating_value INT,
  comment TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE comments (
  comment_id INT,
  customer_id INT,
  product_id INT,
  comment TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE ratings (
  rating_id INT,
  entity_id INT,
  entity_type VARCHAR(50),
  rating INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
